    Author:
    rajasrikar - Build the Rule space first. Default can be a File load - Validate each rule space, criteria format to make sure all rules have a condition and action to perform - loop thru the each Criteria, then Call Basic Validation function, Evaluate the Condition, then Take Action of Either OnMatch, or on UnMatch
